{"tid":620080,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人知邊間醫院有呢種手術做","createTime":"2018-04-07T09:07:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-08T18:43:58.000Z","uid":180913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"161c178c65087b3f15a891ff14713cc308900572","tid":620080,"uid":180913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T09:07:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/spot/20170429/505496\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fspot%2F20170429%2F505496&d=oOx0PQo6li7FOOuXmjG%2ByNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=534cb922\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fspot%2F20170429%2F505496&h=7a9a43cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/spot/20170429/505496</a><br />\n<br />\n瑪麗醫院於二○一五年引入亞洲首部高強度聚焦超聲波儀器，為病人消融甲狀腺增生組織，不留疤痕，毋須全身麻醉，最重要是可以保存甲狀腺功能。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我個病情持續左3年，成日都發燒同心臟好唔舒服<br />\n， 眼凸凸到 情緒低落到今年咩人約都唔肯出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最近 減咗藥搞到我好唔舒服臨時入診所拎藥食<br />\n<br />\n我去左瑪麗 個期去到2019年先見醫生，<br />\n之後 因為減咗藥搞到 心臟好唔舒服入左街邊d診所問，個醫生都唔知 而家最新係可以唔洗開刀，建議我做番傳統即係開刀留 刀疤個種。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想問下邊間私院有得做？我想快d做呢個手術<br />\n定我可以send email 去各大醫院問?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nthx"},{"pid":"f1f9bf7757b550c261ff488621154beddd8a42e4","tid":620080,"uid":1524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T09:12:12.000Z","msg":"你試下打電話去D醫院D外科部門問下"},{"pid":"1fcc69ad2da8eba70946aaf4b1b9a0726eb37927","tid":620080,"uid":126073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T18:41:16.000Z","msg":"香港得瑪麗有"},{"pid":"85b1ec46b113a51a3eca3820f993315ee055027f","tid":620080,"uid":180913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1fcc69ad2da8eba70946aaf4b1b9a0726eb37927","tid":620080,"uid":126073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T18:41:16.000Z","msg":"香港得瑪麗有"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T18:43:58.000Z","msg":"我<img 